quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Attributes[/h1]

The [b]attr()[/b] method also allows us to set a value for an attribute by specifying it as the second parameter. 
For example: [code format="js" codeId="1105"]$(function() {
  $("a").[b]attr[/b]("href", "http://www.jquery.com");
});[/code]
[note]This will change the [b]href [/b]attribute of the <a> element to the provided value.[/note]
